<th scope="col" class="org-left">cost</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left">sent</td>
<td class="org-left">cost</td>
<td class="org-left">sent</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">cost</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>



<div id="outline-container-org230ca04" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org230ca04">Escalado</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org230ca04">
<p>
Cambia el tama√±o del objeto.
</p>

<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-right" />

<col  class="org-right" />

<col  class="org-right" />
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th scope="col" class="org-right">k</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-right">0</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-right">0</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-right">0</td>
<td class="org-right">k</td>
<td class="org-right">0</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-right">0</td>
<td class="org-right">0</td>
<td class="org-right">k</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>




<p>
Ejemplo de c√≥mo aplicar una transformaci√≥n de escalado y rotaci√≥n:
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> <span style="color: #89DDFF;">from</span> OpenGL.GL <span style="color: #89DDFF;">import</span> *
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> <span style="color: #89DDFF;">from</span> OpenGL.GLU <span style="color: #89DDFF;">import</span> *
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> 
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> glPushMatrix<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>         <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Guardar la matriz actual</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> glTranslatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>1.0, 0.0, 0.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Traslaci&#243;n</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> glRotatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>45, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Rotaci&#243;n de 45 grados</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> glScalef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>2.0, 2.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>      <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Escalar el objeto</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> draw_triangle<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>              <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Dibujar el objeto transformado</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> glPopMatrix<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>         <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Restaurar la matriz original</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>





<div id="outline-container-orga348852" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orga348852">Introducci√≥n a la Iluminaci√≥n en OpenGL</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orga348852">
<p>
OpenGL utiliza un modelo de iluminaci√≥n basado en f√≠sica simplificada
que simula c√≥mo la luz interact√∫a con las superficies. Este modelo
considera tres componentes principales de luz: <b><b>ambiente</b></b>, <b><b>difusa</b></b> y
<b><b>especular</b></b>.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org074a793" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org074a793">Conceptos Fundamentales</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org074a793">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4deeda3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4deeda3">Componentes de la Luz</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org4deeda3">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org3265759" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org3265759">Luz Ambiente (Ambient)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org3265759">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Iluminaci√≥n uniforme que llega a todas las superficies por igual</li>
<li>Simula la luz que rebota m√∫ltiples veces en el entorno</li>
<li>No tiene direcci√≥n</li>
<li>Evita que las zonas sin luz directa queden completamente negras</li>
</ul>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_ambient</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.3, 0.3, 0.3, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Gris claro</span>
glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_AMBIENT, light_ambient<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orga368c44" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orga368c44">Luz Difusa (Diffuse)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orga368c44">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Luz principal que depende del √°ngulo entre la superficie y la fuente de luz</li>
<li>Crea el efecto de volumen y forma</li>
<li>Sigue la Ley de Lambert: Intensidad = cos(√°ngulo)</li>
<li>Es la componente m√°s importante para dar forma a los objetos</li>
</ul>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_diffuse</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Blanco brillante</span>
glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_DIFFUSE, light_diffuse<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org233908d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org233908d">Luz Especular (Specular)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org233908d">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Crea brillos y reflejos en superficies brillantes</li>
<li>Depende del √°ngulo entre el observador y el reflejo</li>
<li>Simula materiales brillantes como metal o pl√°stico</li>
<li>Requiere configurar tambi√©n el material del objeto</li>
</ul>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_specular</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Blanco puro</span>
glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_SPECULAR, light_specular<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Tambi&#233;n configurar material</span>
glMaterialfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT, GL_SPECULAR, <span style="color: #f78c6c;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #f78c6c;">]</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
glMaterialf<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT, GL_SHININESS, 100.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">0-128</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgf971796" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgf971796">F√≥rmula de Iluminaci√≥n</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgf971796">
<p>
La intensidad final en un p√≠xel se calcula como:
</p>

<pre class="example" id="orge6dec5e">
I_total = I_ambiente + I_difusa + I_especular

Donde:
I_ambiente = luz_ambiente √ó material_ambiente
I_difusa   = luz_difusa √ó material_difuso √ó cos(Œ∏)
I_especular = luz_especular √ó material_especular √ó cos(Œ±)^shininess

Œ∏ = √°ngulo entre normal y direcci√≥n de luz
Œ± = √°ngulo entre direcci√≥n de reflejo y direcci√≥n al observador
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgafde0f7" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgafde0f7">Tipos de Luces</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgafde0f7">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8d107ef" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org8d107ef">Luz Posicional (Point Light)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org8d107ef">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0316fdf" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org0316fdf">Descripci√≥n</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org0316fdf">
<p>
Una luz que emite desde un punto espec√≠fico en todas direcciones, como una bombilla.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org1029982" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org1029982">Caracter√≠sticas</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org1029982">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Tiene una posici√≥n en el espacio 3D</li>
<li>La intensidad puede disminuir con la distancia (atenuaci√≥n)</li>
<li>W = 1.0 en el vector de posici√≥n</li>
<li>Crea sombras radiales (si se implementan sombras)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgc874eca" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc874eca">C√≥digo</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgc874eca">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">setup_point_light</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHTING<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Posici&#243;n: [X, Y, Z, W]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">W = 1.0 indica luz posicional</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_position</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>3.0, 2.0, 3.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Colores</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_ambient</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.3, 0.3, 0.3, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_diffuse</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_specular</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_POSITION, light_position<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_AMBIENT, light_ambient<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_DIFFUSE, light_diffuse<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_SPECULAR, light_specular<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgf6f114f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgf6f114f">Visualizaci√≥n</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgf6f114f">
<pre class="example" id="orgeb378fc">
         Y
         |
         |   ‚ú® Luz (3, 2, 3)
         |  /|\
         | / | \  Rayos en todas direcciones
         |/  |  \
        /|   |   \
       / |   |    \
      /__|___|_____\_____ X
     /   |   ‚óè     \
    Z    |  Objeto  \
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org52935ed" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org52935ed">Casos de uso</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org52935ed">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>L√°mparas</li>
<li>Velas</li>
<li>Focos de luz</li>
<li>Iluminaci√≥n interior</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgdd383eb" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgdd383eb">Luz Direccional (Directional Light)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgdd383eb">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc3eb88a" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc3eb88a">Descripci√≥n</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgc3eb88a">
<p>
Una luz infinitamente lejana que emite rayos paralelos, como el sol.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orge91cd33" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge91cd33">Caracter√≠sticas</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orge91cd33">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>No tiene posici√≥n, solo direcci√≥n</li>
<li>Todos los rayos son paralelos</li>
<li>W = 0.0 en el vector de posici√≥n</li>
<li>No hay atenuaci√≥n por distancia</li>
<li>M√°s eficiente computacionalmente</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgcaf9691" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgcaf9691">C√≥digo</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgcaf9691">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">setup_directional_light</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHTING<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Direcci&#243;n: [X, Y, Z, W]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">W = 0.0 indica luz direccional</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_direction</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, -1.0, 0.5, 0.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">El vector indica la direcci&#243;n de donde VIENE la luz</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">(1, -1, 0.5) = viene de arriba-derecha-adelante</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_diffuse</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, 0.95, 0.8, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Amarillo c&#225;lido (sol)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_ambient</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.4, 0.4, 0.4, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_POSITION, light_direction<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_DIFFUSE, light_diffuse<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_AMBIENT, light_ambient<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orga6519b1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orga6519b1">Visualizaci√≥n</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orga6519b1">
<pre class="example" id="org7ee6927">
    Sol ‚òÄÔ∏è (infinitamente lejos)
     |  |  |  |  |
     |  |  |  |  |   Rayos paralelos
     ‚Üì  ‚Üì  ‚Üì  ‚Üì  ‚Üì
    _______________
    | | | | | | | |
    | ‚óè | ‚óè | ‚óè | |   Objetos iluminados uniformemente
    |_|_|_|_|_|_|_|
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgbb3caa8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgbb3caa8">Casos de uso</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgbb3caa8">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Luz solar</li>
<li>Escenas exteriores</li>
<li>Iluminaci√≥n general</li>
<li>Escenas muy grandes</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org3c93d81" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org3c93d81">Spotlight (Luz C√≥nica)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org3c93d81">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgff6a58b" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgff6a58b">Descripci√≥n</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgff6a58b">
<p>
Una luz que emite en forma de cono, como un reflector o linterna.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgaf48ec6" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgaf48ec6">Caracter√≠sticas</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgaf48ec6">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Tiene posici√≥n Y direcci√≥n</li>
<li>√Ångulo de apertura configurable (cutoff)</li>
<li>Concentraci√≥n del haz configurable (exponent)</li>
<li>Atenuaci√≥n por distancia</li>
<li>Muy √∫til para efectos dram√°ticos</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgebbbb88" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgebbbb88">Par√°metros</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgebbbb88">
<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-left" />

<col  class="org-left" />

<col  class="org-left" />
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Par√°metro</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Descripci√≥n</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Rango</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left"><code>GL_SPOT_DIRECTION</code></td>
<td class="org-left">Direcci√≥n del cono</td>
<td class="org-left">Vector [x,y,z]</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left"><code>GL_SPOT_CUTOFF</code></td>
<td class="org-left">√Ångulo de apertura</td>
<td class="org-left">0-90¬∞ o 180¬∞ (omni)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left"><code>GL_SPOT_EXPONENT</code></td>
<td class="org-left">Concentraci√≥n</td>
<td class="org-left">0-128</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgdb4e83e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgdb4e83e">C√≥digo</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgdb4e83e">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">setup_spotlight</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHTING<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Posici&#243;n del foco</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">light_position</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.0, 4.0, 2.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Direcci&#243;n hacia donde apunta (vector normalizado)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">spot_direction</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.0, -1.0, -0.5<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">&#193;ngulo del cono (grados)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">spot_cutoff</span> = 30.0  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">0-90 o 180 (180=desactiva spotlight)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Concentraci&#243;n del haz</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">0   = borde suave, disperso</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">128 = borde duro, concentrado</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">spot_exponent</span> = 20.0
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_POSITION, light_position<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_SPOT_DIRECTION, spot_direction<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightf<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_SPOT_CUTOFF, spot_cutoff<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightf<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_SPOT_EXPONENT, spot_exponent<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Colores</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_DIFFUSE, <span style="color: #f78c6c;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #f78c6c;">]</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0, GL_AMBIENT, <span style="color: #f78c6c;">[</span>0.1, 0.1, 0.1, 1.0<span style="color: #f78c6c;">]</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

