<div id="outline-container-org3799d69" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org3799d69">Configuraci√≥n de Materiales</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org3799d69">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org06234a1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org06234a1">Propiedades del Material</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org06234a1">
<p>
Los materiales definen c√≥mo las superficies reaccionan a la luz.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org4254627" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org4254627">Material Ambiente</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org4254627">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ffcb6b;">material_ambient</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.2, 0.2, 0.2, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>
glMaterialfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT, GL_AMBIENT, material_ambient<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orge7dd0f0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge7dd0f0">Material Difuso</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orge7dd0f0">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ffcb6b;">material_diffuse</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>0.8, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Rojo mate</span>
glMaterialfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT, GL_DIFFUSE, material_diffuse<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org7ed3bbd" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org7ed3bbd">Material Especular</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org7ed3bbd">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ffcb6b;">material_specular</span> = <span style="color: #c792ea;">[</span>1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">]</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Brillos blancos</span>
glMaterialfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT, GL_SPECULAR, material_specular<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org9fcbf87" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9fcbf87">Shininess (Brillo)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org9fcbf87">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">0   = superficie mate, difusa</span>
<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">128 = superficie muy brillante, pulida</span>
<span style="color: #ffcb6b;">shininess</span> = 100.0
glMaterialf<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT, GL_SHININESS, shininess<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
