<div id="outline-container-orgafc8a33" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgafc8a33">GL<sub>COLOR</sub><sub>MATERIAL</sub></h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgafc8a33">
<p>
Permite usar <code>glColor3f()</code> con iluminaci√≥n:
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python">glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_COLOR_MATERIAL<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
glColorMaterial<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_FRONT_AND_BACK, GL_AMBIENT_AND_DIFFUSE<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Ahora glColor3f afecta ambient y diffuse del material</span>
glColor3f<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>1.0, 0.0, 0.0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Objeto rojo con iluminaci&#243;n</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org2a2a19d" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org2a2a19d">Funciones Principales de OpenGL</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org2a2a19d">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org62b3d73" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org62b3d73">Activaci√≥n del Sistema</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org62b3d73">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Activar iluminaci&#243;n global</span>
glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHTING<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Activar luces individuales (GL_LIGHT0 a GL_LIGHT7)</span>
glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
glEnable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT1<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Desactivar</span>
glDisable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHTING<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
glDisable<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_LIGHT0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org2111adb" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org2111adb">Configuraci√≥n de Luces</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org2111adb">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Par&#225;metros vectoriales (4 valores)</span>
glLightfv<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>luz, par&#225;metro, valor<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Par&#225;metros escalares (1 valor)</span>
glLightf<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>luz, par&#225;metro, valor<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>

