<div id="outline-container-orgf900887" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgf900887">Diferencia entre Mover Objeto vs Mover C√°mara</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgf900887">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf4ab29d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgf4ab29d">Moviendo el OBJETO (tu c√≥digo actual)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgf4ab29d">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">C&#225;mara FIJA en (0, 0, -5) mirando al origen</span>
glLoadIdentity<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
glTranslatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>0, 0, -5<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>      <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">&#8592; C&#225;mara fija</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">OBJETO rota</span>
glRotatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>rotation, 0, 1, 0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">&#8592; Objeto gira</span>
draw_object<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org275905f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org275905f">Diagrama</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org275905f">
<pre class="example" id="orgb329c41">
    üëÅÔ∏è C√°mara (fija)
     |
     | mira hacia
     ‚Üì
     ‚óè ‚Üª  Objeto ROTA
     
La c√°mara est√° quieta, el objeto gira
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org250ad7d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org250ad7d">Moviendo la C√ÅMARA (objeto fijo)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org250ad7d">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">C&#193;MARA rota alrededor del objeto</span>
glLoadIdentity<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Alejar c&#225;mara</span>
glTranslatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>0, 0, -5<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">C&#193;MARA rota (invirtiendo la rotaci&#243;n)</span>
glRotatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>rotation, 0, 1, 0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">&#8592; C&#225;mara orbita</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Objeto FIJO</span>
draw_object<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgcff3fe2" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgcff3fe2">Diagrama</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgcff3fe2">
<pre class="example" id="org4b40394">
       ‚óè Objeto (fijo)
      /
     /
    üëÅÔ∏è ‚Üª  C√°mara ORBITA
    
El objeto est√° quieto, la c√°mara gira alrededor
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org771fe6a" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org771fe6a">C√≥digo Completo de Ejemplo</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org771fe6a">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">MODO 1: Rotar OBJETO (c&#225;mara fija)</span>
<span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">render_rotating_object</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glMatrixMode<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_MODELVIEW<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLoadIdentity<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">1. Posicionar c&#225;mara (fija)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glTranslatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>0, 0, -5<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">2. Rotar OBJETO</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glRotatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>angle, 0, 1, 0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">3. Dibujar</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   draw_sphere<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">MODO 2: Rotar C&#193;MARA (objeto fijo)</span>
<span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">render_orbiting_camera</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glMatrixMode<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_MODELVIEW<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLoadIdentity<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">1. Rotar C&#193;MARA (invertir rotaci&#243;n)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glRotatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>-angle, 0, 1, 0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">2. Alejar c&#225;mara</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glTranslatef<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>0, 0, -5<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">3. Dibujar objeto (fijo en origen)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   draw_sphere<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>

<span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">MODO 3: Usar gluLookAt (m&#225;s intuitivo para c&#225;mara)</span>
<span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">render_with_lookat</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glMatrixMode<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>GL_MODELVIEW<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLoadIdentity<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Calcular posici&#243;n de c&#225;mara en &#243;rbita</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">cam_x</span> = 5 * math.sin<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>math.radians<span style="color: #f78c6c;">(</span>angle<span style="color: #f78c6c;">)</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ffcb6b;">cam_z</span> = 5 * math.cos<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>math.radians<span style="color: #f78c6c;">(</span>angle<span style="color: #f78c6c;">)</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">gluLookAt(ojo_x, ojo_y, ojo_z, </span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;">#           </span><span style="color: #556369;">mira_x, mira_y, mira_z,</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;">#           </span><span style="color: #556369;">arriba_x, arriba_y, arriba_z)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   gluLookAt<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>cam_x, 0, cam_z,  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Posici&#243;n de c&#225;mara</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> 0, 0, 0,          <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Mira al origen</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> 0, 1, 0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>          <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Vector "arriba"</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Objeto fijo en origen</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   draw_sphere<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org45e935b" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org45e935b">Resumen</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org45e935b">
<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
