</div>
<div id="outline-container-org297d37f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org297d37f">Luz B√°sica</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org297d37f">
<pre class="example" id="orgbdd1360">
Posici√≥n: [2, 3, 2, 1]
Ambient:  [0.3, 0.3, 0.3, 1]
Diffuse:  [1, 1, 1, 1]
Specular: [1, 1, 1, 1]
</pre>
</div>
</div>

