El c√≥digo de la escena base se encuentra en la funci√≥n <code>draw_scene()</code>. Este es el bloque que modificaremos en cada tarea.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python" id="orga71c1eb"><span style="color: #89DDFF;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">draw_scene</span><span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">... (c&#243;digo de limpieza)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   glLoadIdentity<span style="color: #c792ea;">()</span>

<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">****** LA FUNCI&#211;N CLAVE ******</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   gluLookAt<span style="color: #c792ea;">(</span>9, 10, 15,  <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Posici&#243;n de la c&#225;mara (Eye)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> 0, 0, 0,    <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Punto al que mira (Center)</span>
<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span> 0, 1, 0<span style="color: #c792ea;">)</span>    <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">Vector hacia arriba (Up)</span>

<span style="background-color: #1C262B;"> </span>   <span style="color: #556369;"># </span><span style="color: #556369;">... (c&#243;digo de dibujo de casas y suelo)</span>
</pre>
</div>

